Just a quick review about of how this game is cool playing:
1- an kind of a RPG where you feel the difficulty when advancing to higher areas, as monster seems to almost wipe out your team;
2- funny fighting moves and specials that makes you go crazy;
3- collecting weapons and clothes. Man, srsly. Go for it. You'll may like such unique visual character with such vestments;
4-  though having a bit of grinding, it is worth later on as to pass incredible hard bosses;
5- Hard Difficulty is Hard. I know because I did get to the end of it (and with a bit of luck too). Good luck with that xD;
6- and, .. well .. it's free x3
